Wildblood seeds may be grown in hop patches. Planting requires 4 seeds.

Wildblood seeds are dropped by Ogres, Moss giants, Ice warriors, Mountain trolls, and other monsters. Olivia in Draynor Village square will buy Wildblood seeds, but only if players have sold to her, and they can be pickpocketed nearby from a Master Farmer and Seed Stalls.

A nearby gardener will watch over your growing Wildblood hops at the cost of one Nasturtium.

When fully grown, the player can pick the crops and use them to brew into Slayer's respite. See Brewing for a more detailed explanation.

Wildblood seeds are also useful for hunting with birdhouses on Fossil Island.

Wildblood seeds are dropped by [[Ogre]]s, [[Moss giant]]s, [[Ice warrior]]s, [[Mountain troll]]s, and other [[monster]]s. A nearby gardener will watch over your growing [[Wildblood hops]] at the cost of one [[Nasturtiums|Nasturtium]].

When fully grown, the player can pick the crops and use them to [[Brewing|brew]] into [[Slayer's respite]]. See [[Cooking#Brewing|Brewing]] for a more detailed explanation.

Wildblood seeds are also useful for hunting with [[birdhouses]] on [[Fossil Island]].
